shelldone (0.2.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Multi-AI CLI hook support: Codex CLI, Gemini CLI, GitHub Copilot CLI, Cursor
  * Per-AI toggle system (shelldone toggle claude off, etc.)
  * Shared hook library (lib/ai-hook-common.sh)
  * Auto-detect and install all AI hooks (shelldone setup ai-hooks)
  * Uninstall now removes all AI CLI hooks

